{"tid":296020,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老母想拆散我同女朋友","createTime":"2017-06-24T08:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T06:24:39.000Z","uid":17248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28c3f8f332cedebde67d12bf5736ff5d9824fca6","tid":296020,"uid":17248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T08:51:10.000Z","msg":"之前見同女朋友穩定左<br />\n開始傾下結婚啲野<br />\n點知老母乜都bam<br />\n講埋啲難聽說勸我地諗清楚先<br />\n之前最好笑就係講埋啲睇唔起人既說話<br />\n仲問係咪女朋友教我同佢講話要結婚<br />\n真係好撚心計囉屌<br />\n自問自己從來唔會睇唔起人<br />\n都唔知點解會有個咁既老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7888e7e229072b4ddd4c8c05cba28ab1f280db4d","tid":296020,"uid":6957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T08:57:00.000Z","msg":"你會唔會想分手？"},{"pid":"5f2a561b9e276fe9a11baf9a378199e2e0b0c8a1","tid":296020,"uid":43231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T08:57:38.000Z","msg":"結得成都預左第日婆媳關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd0ad65d3ee1d20d9d013aef71ded8b68017d36","tid":296020,"uid":66915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:00:40.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔好理個老母"},{"pid":"cdd8018e64b90d98e84ee169246eaef3a92ae807","tid":296020,"uid":91732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:03:27.000Z","msg":"呢啲第日結完婚有排煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e4acc9040de4532a2880d1261ef6fca3851258","tid":296020,"uid":36770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"[quote]<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樓主係大陸狗黎(已自認)</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/12/161112_2d962b7cb80e281c2fa2573829c89a1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F12%2F161112_2d962b7cb80e281c2fa2573829c89a1e.jpg&h=4ed886d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個係樓主之前個名-連尼住(大佬)</span></strong></span><br />\n讀垃圾OU HD，打字用拼音。<br />\n之後俾巴打圍屌，死不悔改之餘，<br />\n仲笑鳩人讀書少，唔抵得人識打拼音！<br />\n堅稱自己係土生土長嘅香港人喎~~<br />\n<br />\n就算識打字嗰陣都要轉channel去諗嗰個字嘅蝗語點讀，再打出嚟。<br />\n點都慢過用倉頡速成就咁諗點打好撚多<br />\n除非佢本身就係蝗語channel，又或者講慣蝗語<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/12/163227_7529c4fae71b5dd7ff9beea275ef5ec9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F12%2F163227_7529c4fae71b5dd7ff9beea275ef5ec9.jpg&h=ca5c499d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本係大陸仔打啲字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唸又窩又奔，都唔知佢打乜柒！<br />\n你全家奔緊落地獄呀支那狗！！！！！<br />\n下世咪撚再落黎香港，生生世世做中蟈人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過追擊之下，終於承認自己係支那狗，<br />\n並聲稱自己永遠都唔上LIHKG"}]}